On Ubuntu:

1. Install Tomcat6: sudo apt-get -install tomcat6

  1.1 cp var/www/scmextern/JavaBridge.war /var/lib/tomcat6/webapps

2. In /var/lib/tomcat6/webapps/Javabridge/WEB-INF:

 2.1 sudo mkdir classes
 2.2 sudo cp /var/www/scm/java/bin/* .

3. In /var/lib/tomcat6/webapps/Javabridge/WEB-INF/lib:

 3.1 sudo rm lucene*
 3.2 sudo cp /var/www/scm/java/lib/* .

4. sudo  service tomcat6 restart

On Windows:

1. To start up tomcat6: startup.bat
